snippet.title: Best VGM 2060 - Mega Man 9 - Magma Burning (Magma Man Stage)
snippet.description:

Wii / Xbox 360 / Playstation 3
Mega Man 9 (2008)
Magma Burning (Magma Man Stage)
Ippo Yamada, Ryo Kawakami, Yu Shimoda, Hiroki Isogai & Ogeretsu Kun
